headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid TECH and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Shareholders of Bio-Techne would probably like to forget the past six months even happened. The stock dropped 21% and now trades at $57.45. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
